reviewText: I like this Dvd because it has SpongeBob Squarepants.

ACTUAL LIST OF EPISODES:

Spongebob Squarepants Christmas:

- Christmas Who? (double length episode)

+ 8 "Merry Episodes"

- Procrastination

- Snowball Effect

- Survival of the Idiots

- Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy IV

- Chocolate with Nuts

- As Seen on TV

- Pizza Delivery

- Squeaky Boots

Dora's Christmas:

- A Present for Santa

- Rapido Tico!

- Quack! Quack!

- School Pet

Blue's Room Holiday Wishes:

- Blue's Room Holiday

- Can You Help?

- Look Carefully...

- Patience

~ A pretty good collection for younger ones - I wouldn't pay full price, as all of the Spongebob episodes, and likely the Nick Jr. ones as well, play on Nickelodeon frequently, and there aren't any good special features

I am very curious about this dvd--or should I say three dvd's--they need to list some of the tv shows included in this set..

I mean for the money it would be nice to know what you are getting...
